legalText: BASIC INFORMATION ABOUT PERSONAL DATA PROTECTION
legalAddresseeText: Personal data will be exclusively processed by the society. This society does not transfer any kind of personal data to third parties
legalFinalityText: Personal data will be processed with the finality of verify the identity of the subject and if it is suitable to be accepted in the society
legalLegitimacyText: Execution of a contract and manage the communication between customer and administrators
legalRightsText: Every member of the society has the rights to:
legalRights1: - Right to get a confirmation of the responsible of the data processing to know if the data is being treated in a correct way, get a copy of the data, and being informed of the guarantees in the transfer of the data
legalRights2: - Right to update and add data
legalRights3: - Right to delete data when it is not necessary for its finality, illicit treatment, or the responsible posted the data.
legalRights4: - Right to limit the processing of data in case of illicit treatment
legalRights5: - Right to be informed about the data processed and who is processing that data
legalRights6: - Right to receive its personal data in an appropriate format in order to transfer them to another responsible, in case of legitimate use
legalRights7: - Right to object to the processing of data when it is used for public interest, direct marketing, or profiling.
legalResponsibleText: The responsible for the data processing is only the administrator of the Society
